# Code quality (CV Studio)

## Commands

| Goal | Command |
| --- | --- |
| Full gate | `pnpm run check` |
| Lint only | `pnpm run lint` (Oxlint **--deny-warnings** + markdownlint) |
| Fix lint where supported | `pnpm run lint:fix` |
| Format | `pnpm run format` |
| Verify format | `pnpm run format:check` |
| Types only | `pnpm run typecheck` |
| Production build | `pnpm run build` |

After substantive edits, prefer **`pnpm run check`** before hand-off.

## Style

- **No `any`** — use proper types or `unknown`.
- **Await promises** — no floating promises (Oxlint).
- **Unused** — remove or prefix with `_`.
- **Imports** — prefer `import type { … }` for type-only imports.
- **Discriminated unions** — handle all variants; use a `never` exhaustiveness check in `default` when switching on section `kind` or similar.
- **Imports at top** — no inline `import()` except intentional lazy/load splits.
- **Filenames** — follow existing files under `src/` (mostly PascalCase for React components).

## Config

- Oxlint: `@.oxlintrc.json`
- Formatter: oxfmt (via `pnpm run format`)
